---
title: Chorizo and Sweet Pepper Tacos with Lime Crema and Salsa Fresca
description: A satisfying plate of tacos is just what the doctor ordered! For these handhelds, roasted peppers and onions are paired with seasoned ground chorizo, zesty lime crema and a homemade salsa fresca.
